Yogi: Shri Mataji said we have done already 300 names, and that we will have our food, then we will continue for the rest.

Shri Mataji: Those people who were living in the south should go and help, and bring these things from downstairs and put them up here. Because so many cannot be fitted downstairs. You can open these plates and things, and some of you can put it up. Keep it in the veranda; keep it in the veranda.

You all can have a wash or something, if you want to have it. And come along for lunch.